d to, you can press ESC to cancel the command.\nTo see examples of some R error messages with explanations see [here](https://github.com/noamross/zero-dependency-problems/issues/7)","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"<a id=\"0\"></a>\n<font color=\"black\" size=+2.5><b>Starters</b></font>\n\n<a href=\"#top\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" role=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"true\" style=\"color:white\" data-toggle=\"popover\" title=\"go to Colors\">Go to TOC</a>","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"titanic=titanic[complete.cases(titanic),]","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-11-28T11:18:12.665223Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-11-28T11:18:12.666377Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-11-28T11:18:12.681887Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":14,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"First, let's get a sense of the data's structure with the str() command.\n","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"str(titanic)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-11-28T11:18:14.514901Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-11-28T11:18:14.517119Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-11-28T11:18:14.546204Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":15,"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"tibble [183 × 12] (S3: tbl_df/tbl/data.frame)\n $ PassengerId: num [1:183] 2 4 7 11 12 22 24 28 53 55 ...\n $ Survived   : num [1:183] 1 1 0 1 1 1 1 0 1 0 ...\n $ Pclass     : num [1:183] 1 1 1 3 1 2 1 1 1 1 ...\n $ Name       : chr [1:183] \"Cumings, Mrs. John Bradley (Florence Briggs Thayer)\" \"Futrelle, Mrs. Jacques Heath (Lily May Peel)\" \"McCarthy, Mr. Timothy J\" \"Sandstrom, Miss. Marguerite Rut\" ...\n $ Sex        : chr [1:183] \"female\" \"female\" \"male\" \"female\" ...\n $ Age        : num [1:183] 38 35 54 4 58 34 28 19 49 65 ...\n $ SibSp      : num [1:183] 1 1 0 1 0 0 0 3 1 0 ...\n $ Parch      : num [1:183] 0 0 0 1 0 0 0 2 0 1 ...\n $ Ticket     : chr [1:183] \"PC 17599\" \"113803\" \